ce said that he loves to travel a lot, and his favourite places to travel include Singapore, England, Dubai, and South Korea. Channi performed the bhangra during an occasion in Kapurthala, Punjab, just a few days after being appointed as Chief Minister of Punjab. A clip of the newly appointed Chief Minister showing his dance steps on a podium with a folk performer became popular on social media. Channi attempted to establish positive connections with Rahul Gandhi with the support of CP Joshi, a senior congress member, after joining the Indian National Congress in 2010. Income and Net Worth On Monday, Channi submitted his application for the Bhadaur post in the Barnala region. The Congress nominated Channi for one of two Assembly seats, one of which is Chamkaur Sahib. As per his submitted campaign papers, Channi disclosed that he owns assets of around Rs. 9.44 crore. Channi bought a Toyota Fortuner SUV worth Rs. 32.57 lakh (approx.), according to his election papers, whereas his wife, a doctor, owned two cars total of around Rs. 45.99 lakh. According to the document, there is one residential home of 14,062 sq. ft of size in Morinda registered in Channi's identity and another residential property with 13,500 sq. ft in Kharar in Mohali in his wife's name. According to his statement, Channi and his wife's entire obligations, along with a vehicle loan, are nearly equal to the amount of Rs. 88.35 lakh (estimated). Channi has disclosed total earnings of around Rs. 27.84 lakh for 2020-21. Next TopicDhanashree Verma ? prev next ? For Videos Join Our Youtube Channel: Join Now Feedback Send your Feedback to [email protected] Help Others, Please Share Learn Latest Tutorials Splunk SPSS Swagger Transact-SQL Tumblr ReactJS Regex Reinforcement Learning R Programming RxJS React Native Python Design Patterns Python Pillow Python Turtle Keras Preparation Aptitude Reasoning Verbal Ability Interview Questions Company Questions Trending Technologies Artificial Intelligence AWS Selenium 